Package tnote.util.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IncorrectTimeException
    This class is a custom exception thrown when the ending date and time of a task is before its starting date and time.
    InvalidFileNameException
    This class is a custom exception which is thrown when a task with an invalid file name is attempted to be saved in the system
    TaskExistsException
    This class is a custom exception which is thrown when the user tries to add a task which already exists in the system
    TimeClashException
    This class is a custom exception thrown when there is a clash in timings between an existing task in the system and a task the user wants to add
